                        <td>
                        
                            <p><strong>When did you become a Hallmark card hippie? Joy, love, peace. Puke! Where&#39;s the rage, anger, hatred? Reading these lately is like listening to an old preacher drone on and on at Sunday mass.</strong><br/>
ERMINE, GRAND MARAIS, USA</p>

